\begin_layout Standard

\series medium
The Stat-Analysis tool ties together results from the Point-Stat, Grid-Stat,
 Ensemble-Stat and Wavelet-Stat tools by providing summary statistical informati
on and a way to filter their STAT output files.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series medium
